12 Sep\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nv070901\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2011-10-28\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n-3631.9\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nLimit c-gahp's time connected to the schedd\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr bgcolor=\"#c8c8c8\">\n<td valign=\"top\">\njfrey\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a href=\"tktview?tn=3023,86\">3023</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nresolved\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nenhance\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n3\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 May\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 Oct\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nv070901\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nConfigurable poll intervals for Condor-G based on number of jobs\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr bgcolor=\"#c8c8c8\">\n<td valign=\"top\">\njfrey\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a href=\"tktview?tn=3016,86\">3016</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nresolved\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\ndefect\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n3\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 May\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 Aug\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nv070901\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nblahp canceling of completed job causes a failure\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr bgcolor=\"#cacae5\">\n<td valign=\"top\">\njfrey\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a href=\"tktview?tn=2574,86\">2574</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\ndefer\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nenhance\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n4\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2011 Oct\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2020 Jun\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nOptimize job submission to the schedd\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr bgcolor=\"#c8c8c8\">\n<td valign=\"top\">\njfrey\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a href=\"tktview?tn=3015,86\">3015</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nresolved\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nenhance\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n4\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 May\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2013 Jan\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nv070903\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nGAHP should set GLOBUS_LOCATION for new blahp\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr bgcolor=\"#c8c8c8\">\n<td valign=\"top\">\njfrey\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a href=\"tktview?tn=3025,86\">3025</a></td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nresolved\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nenhance\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n5\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 Jun\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\n2012 Sep\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nv070901\n</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\u00a0</td>\n<td valign=\"top\">\nAutodetect proxy-location\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n\n\n<p></p><ul>\n<li>To be secure, clients (i.e. submitters) must list the DNs of the servers (i.e. schedds) that they trust.  This is not ideal.  What would be better is to have an authorization mode that just checks that the remote identity is a valid SSL server with a matching hostname.  Most of a solution has been implemented for this in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1605\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1605'); return false;\" title=\"support host certificate DNS name validation\">#1605</a></span>.\n\n<p></p></li><li>GUMS support.  This has been dealt with in <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1834\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1834'); return false;\" title=\"Add support for GSI authz mapping callout\">#1834</a></span>.\n\n<p></p></li><li>site customization - need a callout that allows the site to modify the user job before it runs, similarly to how people do things in the Globus jobmanager condor.pm. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"abandoned\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1364\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1364'); return false;\" title=\"job queue hooks\">#1364</a></span>\n\n<p></p></li><li>performance - in my tests of 7.3.2, I could not get more than 0.1 jobs/s to run through Condor-C.  Perhaps I didn't understand how to tune it, or perhaps some things have been improved since then.  If not, this would need attention.\n\n<p></p></li><li>reliability - do jobs randomly go on hold?  At one time, this was a problem.</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2011-Oct-03 17:14:52 by bbockelm:</em> <br/>\n\n<ul>\n<li>For customization, why not take the approach of using the <span class=\"wiki\"><a href=\"wiki?p=JobRouter\" title=\"Job Router\">JobRouter</a></span> to do the job transformation?  That way, we have something that at least is scalability-tested.x\n   *: It would get even better with the multicast-router patch\n</li><li>For scalability: here's an issue: <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2279\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2279'); return false;\" title=\"Condor-C Failure in the OSG Summer School\">#2279</a></span>\n</li><li>For security: Should we allow end-users to play around with attributes via condor_qedit?  Is there any need for more fine-grained permission there?</li></ul>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=1605\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('1605'); return false;\" title=\"support host certificate DNS name validation\">#1605</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nsupport host certificate DNS name validation</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2406\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2406'); return false;\" title=\"Input files are transferred with output when job is spooled\">#2406</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nInput files are transferred with output when job is spooled</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"defer\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2574\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2574'); return false;\" title=\"Optimize job submission to the schedd\">#2574</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nOptimize job submission to the schedd</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2575\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2575'); return false;\" title=\"Limit c-gahp's time connected to the schedd\">#2575</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nLimit c-gahp's time connected to the schedd</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3015\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3015'); return false;\" title=\"GAHP should set GLOBUS_LOCATION for new blahp\">#3015</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nGAHP should set GLOBUS_LOCATION for new blahp</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3016\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3016'); return false;\" title=\"blahp canceling of completed job causes a failure\">#3016</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<